msgid "1. Module resolution"
msgstr "1. 모듈 해결"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:85
msgid ""
"Perry's resolver "
"([`crates/perry/src/commands/compile/resolve.rs`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/src/commands/compile/resolve.rs))"
" walks each search path looking for `node_modules/mysql2/`:"
msgstr ""
"Perry의 리졸버 "
"([`crates/perry/src/commands/compile/resolve.rs`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/src/commands/compile/resolve.rs))는"
" 각 검색 경로를 따라 `node_modules/mysql2/`를 찾습니다:"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:89
msgid ""
"**If `node_modules/mysql2/package.json` exists with a `perry.nativeLibrary` "
"block**: parse the manifest, treat the package as a native binding. Skip "
"layers (c) and (d)."
msgstr ""
"**`node_modules/mysql2/package.json`이 `perry.nativeLibrary` 블록과 함께 존재하는 "
"경우**: 매니페스트를 파싱하고 패키지를 네이티브 바인딩으로 취급합니다. 레이어 (c)와 (d)를 건너뜁니다."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:92
msgid ""
"**If `node_modules/mysql2/` exists without a `perry.nativeLibrary` block**: "
"this is a JS-only npm package; fall through to the V8 / JS interpretation "
"path (separate compilation flow)."
msgstr ""
"**`node_modules/mysql2/`가 `perry.nativeLibrary` 블록 없이 존재하는 경우**: 이는 JS 전용 "
"npm 패키지입니다. V8 / JS 해석 경로로 떨어집니다 (별도의 컴파일 흐름)."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:96
msgid ""
"**If `node_modules/mysql2/` doesn't exist at all**: consult the **well-known"
" table** at "
"[`crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml)."
" The table maps `mysql2` → `perry-ext-mysql2` (a Rust crate that ships in "
"the Perry install). The user didn't `npm install` anything; Perry handles "
"it."
msgstr ""
"**`node_modules/mysql2/`가 전혀 존재하지 않는 경우**: "
"[`crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/crates/perry/well_known_bindings.toml)에"
" 있는 **well-known 테이블**을 참고합니다. 테이블은 `mysql2`를 `perry-ext-mysql2` 크레이트로 "
"매핑합니다."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:102
msgid "**If nothing matches**: compile error pointing at the import line."
msgstr "**일치하는 것이 없는 경우**: import 줄을 가리키는 컴파일 오류."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:104
msgid "2. ABI version check"
msgstr "2. ABI 버전 검사"

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:106
msgid ""
"If the resolved binding has a `perry.nativeLibrary.abiVersion` field "
"(required from v0.6.0 onwards; warning-only in v0.5.x), Perry verifies the "
"declared semver range covers the bundled `perry-ffi` version. A binding "
"declaring `\"0.5\"` loads under any `0.5.x` Perry; one declaring `\"^1.0\"` "
"loads only under `1.x`. Mismatches are a hard compile error with a recipe "
"pointing at the offending package."
msgstr ""
"해결된 바인딩에 `perry.nativeLibrary.abiVersion` 필드가 있다면 (v0.6.0부터 필수, v0.5.x에서는 "
"경고만), Perry는 선언된 semver 범위가 번들된 `perry-ffi` 버전을 다루는지 확인합니다. `\"0.5\"`를 선언하는 "
"바인딩은 perry-ffi 0.5.x를 출하하는 모든 Perry에서 로드되며, 0.6.0에서는 거부됩니다."

