msgid "[`abi.md`](abi.md) — the perry-ffi surface, reference grade."
msgstr "[`abi.md`](abi.md) — perry-ffi 표면, 참조 등급."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:360
msgid ""
"[`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md) — the `perry.nativeLibrary` schema, every"
" field documented."
msgstr ""
"[`manifest-v1.md`](manifest-v1.md) — `perry.nativeLibrary` 스키마, 모든 필드가 문서화됨."

#: src/native-libraries/overview.md:362
msgid ""
"[API reference](../api/reference.md) — auto-generated list of every stdlib "
"symbol Perry implements."
msgstr "[API 참조](../api/reference.md) — Perry가 구현하는 모든 stdlib 심볼의 자동 생성된 목록."

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:1
msgid "Authoring a native binding"
msgstr "네이티브 바인딩 작성"

#: src/native-libraries/authoring-guide.md:3
msgid ""
"Step-by-step guide to writing and publishing a Rust binding that Perry "
"programs can `import` like any npm package."
msgstr "Perry 프로그램이 어떤 npm 패키지처럼 `import`할 수 있는 Rust 바인딩을 작성하고 게시하는 단계별 가이드."

