"[\\#466 Phase 2](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466)는 "
"`perry.nativeLibrary` 매니페스트 사양을 동결하고 해결 시 `abiVersion`을 강제합니다."

#: src/native-libraries/abi.md:163
msgid ""
"[\\#466 Phase 3](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/466) adds `perry "
"native init/validate/prebuild` for scaffolding new wrapper packages."
