#: src/ui/widgets.md:289
msgid "TextArea"
msgstr "TextArea"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:291
msgid ""
"A multi-line text input. Same `(placeholder, onChange)` signature as "
"`TextField` but renders as a multi-line box."
msgstr ""
"여러 줄 텍스트 입력. `TextField`와 동일한 `(placeholder, onChange)` 시그니처지만 여러 줄 박스로 "
"렌더링됩니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:294
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"// demonstrates: TextArea for multi-line input\n"
"// docs: docs/src/ui/widgets.md\n"
"// platforms: macos, linux, windows\n"
"// targets: ios-simulator, web, wasm\n"
"\n"
"import { App, VStack, Text, TextArea, State } from \"perry/ui\"\n"
"\n"
"const content = State(\"\")\n"
"\n"
"App({\n"
"    title: \"TextArea\",\n"
"    width: 500,\n"
"    height: 400,\n"
"    body: VStack(12, [\n"
"        TextArea(\"Enter multi-line text...\", (value: string) => content.set(value)),\n"
"        Text(`Length: ${content.value.length}`),\n"
"    ]),\n"
"})\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:315
msgid "**Helpers:** `textareaSetString`."
msgstr "**헬퍼:** `textareaSetString`."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:317 src/cli/perry-toml.md:108
msgid "Sections"
msgstr "Sections"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:319
msgid ""
"Group controls into labelled sections. Perry has no `Form()` widget — use a "
"`VStack` of `Section(title)`s and attach children via `widgetAddChild`."
msgstr ""
"컨트롤을 라벨이 붙은 섹션으로 그룹화합니다. Perry에는 `Form()` 위젯이 없습니다 — `Section(title)`의 "
"`VStack`을 사용하고 `widgetAddChild`를 통해 자식을 첨부하세요."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:322
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"// demonstrates: Section grouping with widgetAddChild (no Form widget in Perry)\n"
"// docs: docs/src/ui/widgets.md\n"
"// platforms: macos, linux, windows\n"
"// targets: ios-simulator, web, wasm\n"
"\n"
"import {\n"
"    App,\n"
"    VStack,\n"
"    Section,\n"
"    TextField,\n"
"    Toggle,\n"
"    State,\n"
"    widgetAddChild,\n"
"} from \"perry/ui\"\n"
"\n"
"const name = State(\"\")\n"
"const notifications = State(true)\n"
"\n"
"const personal = Section(\"Personal Info\")\n"
"widgetAddChild(personal, TextField(\"Name\", (value: string) => name.set(value)))\n"
"\n"
"const settings = Section(\"Settings\")\n"
"widgetAddChild(\n"
"    settings,\n"
"    Toggle(\"Notifications\", (on: boolean) => notifications.set(on)),\n"
")\n"
"\n"
"App({\n"
"    title: \"Sections\",\n"
"    width: 500,\n"
"    height: 400,\n"
"    body: VStack(16, [personal, settings]),\n"
"})\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:358
msgid "Mobile widgets (issue #553)"
msgstr "모바일 위젯 (issue #553)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:360
msgid "BottomNavigation"
msgstr "BottomNavigation"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:362
msgid ""
"5-tab bottom bar with icon + label + badge per tab. `onSelect(index)` fires "
"when the user taps; `bottomNavSetSelected` is the programmatic counterpart "
"and does NOT fire `onSelect`."
msgstr ""
"탭당 아이콘 + 라벨 + 배지를 가진 5탭 하단 바. 사용자가 탭하면 `onSelect(index)`가 발생합니다; "
"`bottomNavSetSelected`는 프로그램적인 카운터파트이며 `onSelect`를 발생시키지 **않습니다**."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:366
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  BottomNavigation,\n"
"  bottomNavAddItem,\n"
"  bottomNavSetBadge,\n"
"} from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const bar = BottomNavigation((index) => {\n"
"  console.log(\"tab:\", index);\n"
"});\n"
"bottomNavAddItem(bar, \"house\", \"Home\");\n"
"bottomNavAddItem(bar, \"magnifyingglass\", \"Search\");\n"
"bottomNavAddItem(bar, \"bell\", \"Activity\");\n"
"bottomNavSetBadge(bar, 2, \"5\");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:382
msgid ""
"Real on macOS (`NSStackView` + `NSButton` strip with SF Symbol icons), iOS "
"(`UITabBar`), Android (custom `LinearLayout` strip with badge overlay), and "
"GTK4 (`GtkBox` + Adwaita CSS). Stub on Windows, tvOS, visionOS, watchOS."
msgstr ""
"macOS (SF Symbol 아이콘이 있는 `NSStackView` + `NSButton` 스트립), iOS (`UITabBar`), "
"Android (배지 오버레이가 있는 사용자 정의 `LinearLayout` 스트립), GTK4 (`GtkBox` + Adwaita "
"CSS)에서 실제. Windows, tvOS, visionOS, watchOS에서는 스텁."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:387
msgid "ImageGallery"
msgstr "ImageGallery"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:389
msgid ""
"Swipeable, paging carousel of images. Local file paths load synchronously; "
"HTTP/HTTPS URLs are fetched on a background queue and applied on the main "
"thread."
msgstr ""
"스와이프 가능한 페이징 이미지 캐러셀. 로컬 파일 경로는 동기적으로 로드되고; HTTP/HTTPS URL은 백그라운드 큐에서 가져와서 "
"메인 스레드에서 적용됩니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:393
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { ImageGallery, imageGalleryAddImage } from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const gallery = ImageGallery((idx) => console.log(\"page:\", idx));\n"
"imageGalleryAddImage(gallery, \"/photos/01.jpg\", \"Hero shot\");\n"
"imageGalleryAddImage(gallery, \"https://cdn.example/photo2.jpg\", \"Wide angle\");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:401
msgid ""
"Real on macOS (`NSScrollView` paging), iOS (`UIScrollView` with "
"`scrollViewDidEndDecelerating`), Android (`HorizontalScrollView`), GTK4 "
"(`GtkScrolledWindow` + `GtkPicture`). Stub on Windows, tvOS, visionOS, "
"watchOS."
msgstr ""
"macOS (`NSScrollView` 페이징), iOS (`scrollViewDidEndDecelerating`이 있는 "
"`UIScrollView`), Android (`HorizontalScrollView`), GTK4 (`GtkScrolledWindow`"
" + `GtkPicture`)에서 실제. Windows, tvOS, visionOS, watchOS에서는 스텁."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:406
msgid "Pull-to-refresh"
msgstr "Pull-to-refresh"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:408
msgid ""
"Available on `ScrollView` and `LazyVStack`. The `onPull` callback fires once"
" when the user pulls past the threshold; call `scrollviewEndRefreshing` (or "
"`lazyvstackEndRefreshing`) when your async fetch settles to dismiss the "
"spinner."
msgstr ""
"`ScrollView`와 `LazyVStack`에서 사용 가능. `onPull` 콜백은 사용자가 임계값을 넘어 당길 때 한 번 "
"발생합니다; 비동기 가져오기가 정착되면 스피너를 닫기 위해 `scrollviewEndRefreshing` (또는 "
"`lazyvstackEndRefreshing`)을 호출하세요."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:413
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  ScrollView,\n"
"  scrollviewSetRefreshControl,\n"
"  scrollviewEndRefreshing,\n"
"} from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const scroll = ScrollView();\n"
"scrollviewSetRefreshControl(scroll, async () => {\n"
"  await refreshFeed();\n"
"  scrollviewEndRefreshing(scroll);\n"
"});\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:427
msgid ""
"Real on iOS (`UIRefreshControl`). The macOS / Android / GTK4 / Windows "
"desktops have no native pull-to-refresh idiom — they're documented no-ops."
msgstr ""
"iOS (`UIRefreshControl`)에서 실제. macOS / Android / GTK4 / Windows 데스크톱에는 네이티브 "
"pull-to-refresh 관용구가 없습니다 — 그것들은 문서화된 no-op입니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:431
msgid "Infinite scroll (`onScrollEnd`)"
msgstr "무한 스크롤 (`onScrollEnd`)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:433
msgid ""
"Fires once when the user scrolls past `thresholdPx` (or `thresholdItems` for"
" `LazyVStack`) from the bottom; re-arms after the user scrolls back up past "
"the threshold so a single fetch is queued at a time."
msgstr ""
"사용자가 하단에서 `thresholdPx` (또는 `LazyVStack`의 경우 `thresholdItems`)를 지나 스크롤할 때 한 "
"번 발생합니다; 사용자가 임계값을 다시 지나 위로 스크롤하면 다시 활성화되어 한 번에 하나의 가져오기만 큐에 들어갑니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:437
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { ScrollView, scrollviewSetScrollEndCallback } from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const scroll = ScrollView();\n"
"scrollviewSetScrollEndCallback(\n"
"  scroll,\n"
"  () => loadMore(),\n"
"  200, // threshold in pixels from the bottom\n"
");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:448
msgid ""
"Real on every platform that has a scroll view: macOS "
"(`NSViewBoundsDidChangeNotification`), iOS "
"(`UIScrollViewDelegate.scrollViewDidScroll`), Android "
"(`View.OnScrollChangeListener`), GTK4 (`GtkAdjustment::value-changed`), "
"Windows (`WM_VSCROLL` / `WM_MOUSEWHEEL`)."
msgstr ""
"스크롤 뷰가 있는 모든 플랫폼에서 실제: macOS (`NSViewBoundsDidChangeNotification`), iOS "
"(`UIScrollViewDelegate.scrollViewDidScroll`), Android "
"(`View.OnScrollChangeListener`), GTK4 (`GtkAdjustment::value-changed`), "
"Windows (`WM_VSCROLL` / `WM_MOUSEWHEEL`)."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:454
msgid "Platform-specific widgets"
msgstr "플랫폼 특정 위젯"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:456
msgid ""
"These exist only on specific platforms and aren't verified by the cross-"
"platform doc-tests:"
msgstr "이들은 특정 플랫폼에만 존재하며 크로스 플랫폼 doc-tests로 검증되지 않습니다:"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:459
msgid ""
"**`Table(rows, cols, renderer)`** — macOS only. Now supports "
"`tableSetSortColumn`, `tableSetFilterText`, and multi-select since v0.5.636 "
"(#473)."
msgstr ""
"**`Table(rows, cols, renderer)`** — macOS 전용. v0.5.636 (#473) 이후 "
"`tableSetSortColumn`, `tableSetFilterText`, 다중 선택을 지원합니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:462
msgid "**`QRCode(data, size)`** — macOS only. Renders a QR code."
msgstr "**`QRCode(data, size)`** — macOS 전용. QR 코드를 렌더링합니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:463
msgid ""
"**`Canvas(width, height, draw)`** — all desktop platforms. A drawing "
"surface; see [Canvas](canvas.md)."
msgstr ""
"**`Canvas(width, height, draw)`** — 모든 데스크톱 플랫폼. 그리기 표면; [Canvas](canvas.md)"
" 참조."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:465
msgid ""
"**`CameraView()`** — iOS only (other platforms planned). See "
"[Camera](camera.md)."
msgstr "**`CameraView()`** — iOS 전용 (다른 플랫폼은 계획 중). [Camera](camera.md) 참조."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:468
msgid "Combobox (issue #475)"
msgstr "Combobox (issue #475)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:470
msgid ""
"Editable text field with a filterable dropdown of suggestions. macOS uses "
"`NSComboBox` with as-you-type completion; other platforms stub the FFI today"
" (the field falls back to a plain editable field)."
msgstr ""
"필터링 가능한 제안 드롭다운이 있는 편집 가능한 텍스트 필드. macOS는 입력하면서 자동 완성하는 `NSComboBox`를 사용합니다;"
" 다른 플랫폼은 오늘 FFI를 스텁합니다 (필드는 일반 편집 가능한 필드로 폴백됩니다)."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:474
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { Combobox, comboboxAddItem, comboboxGetValue } from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const combo = Combobox(\"\", (v) => console.log(\"picked:\", v));\n"
"comboboxAddItem(combo, \"apple\");\n"
"comboboxAddItem(combo, \"apricot\");\n"
"comboboxAddItem(combo, \"avocado\");\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:483
msgid "TreeView / Outline (issue #480)"
msgstr "TreeView / Outline (issue #480)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:485
msgid ""
"Hierarchical disclosure list. Build the topology bottom-up via `TreeNode`"
msgstr "계층적 공개 목록. `TreeNode`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:486
msgid ""
"`treeNodeAddChild`, then mount it via `TreeView`. macOS uses "
"`NSOutlineView`; other platforms stub."
msgstr ""
"`treeNodeAddChild`로 토폴로지를 상향식으로 빌드한 다음, `TreeView`를 통해 마운트합니다. macOS는 "
"`NSOutlineView`를 사용합니다; 다른 플랫폼은 스텁."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:489
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { TreeNode, treeNodeAddChild, TreeView } from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const dox = TreeNode(\"docs\", \"Documents\");\n"
"treeNodeAddChild(dox, TreeNode(\"doc-1\", \"Resume.pdf\"));\n"
"treeNodeAddChild(dox, TreeNode(\"doc-2\", \"Cover Letter.pdf\"));\n"
"const root = TreeNode(\"root\", \"Files\");\n"
"treeNodeAddChild(root, dox);\n"
"const tree = TreeView(root, (id) => console.log(\"selected:\", id));\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:500
msgid "Calendar (issue #481)"
msgstr "Calendar (issue #481)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:502
msgid ""
"Month-grid date picker. macOS uses `NSDatePicker` in graphical style; other "
"platforms stub. `onChange` receives the selected date as an ISO `yyyy-MM-dd`"
" string."
msgstr ""
"월 그리드 날짜 선택기. macOS는 그래픽 스타일의 `NSDatePicker`를 사용합니다; 다른 플랫폼은 스텁. `onChange`는"
" 선택된 날짜를 ISO `yyyy-MM-dd` 문자열로 받습니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:506
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { Calendar, calendarGetSelectedDate } from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const cal = Calendar(2026, 5, (iso) => console.log(\"date:\", iso));\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:512
msgid "DatePicker (issue #4772)"
msgstr "DatePicker (이슈 #4772)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:514
msgid ""
"Compact field-style date picker — the space-saving complement to the month-"
"grid `Calendar`. Each platform uses its native compact date control: macOS "
"`NSDatePicker` (text-field-and-stepper), iOS / visionOS `UIDatePicker` "
"(`.compact`), Windows `SysDateTimePick32`, Android "
"`android.widget.DatePicker`. GTK4 has no native compact date field, so it "
"reuses `GtkCalendar`; tvOS / watchOS stub. `onChange` receives the selected "
"date as an ISO `yyyy-MM-dd` string."
msgstr ""
"공간 절약형 compact 날짜 선택기 — 월별 그리드 `Calendar`의 공간 절약형 보완 위젯입니다. 각 플랫폼은 자체 네이티브 "
"compact 날짜 컨트롤을 사용합니다: macOS `NSDatePicker` (텍스트 필드 및 스테퍼), iOS / visionOS "
"`UIDatePicker` (`.compact`), Windows `SysDateTimePick32`, Android "
"`android.widget.DatePicker`. GTK4에는 네이티브 compact 날짜 필드가 없으므로 `GtkCalendar`를 "
"재사용하고, tvOS / watchOS는 스텁입니다. `onChange`는 선택된 날짜를 ISO `yyyy-MM-dd` 문자열로 "
"전달합니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:522
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { DatePicker, datePickerGetSelectedDate } from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const picker = DatePicker(2026, 5, (iso) => console.log(\"date:\", iso));\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:528
msgid "Chart (issue #474)"
msgstr "Chart (issue #474)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:530
msgid ""
"Line / bar / pie via CoreGraphics on macOS. `kind` is `0=line`, `1=bar`, "
"`2=pie`. Apple Charts framework / SwiftUI Charts integration on iOS 16+ is a"
" follow-up."
msgstr ""
"macOS의 CoreGraphics를 통한 라인 / 막대 / 파이. `kind`는 `0=라인`, `1=막대`, `2=파이`. iOS "
"16+의 Apple Charts 프레임워크 / SwiftUI Charts 통합은 후속 작업입니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:534
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { Chart, chartAddDataPoint, chartSetTitle } from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const chart = Chart(0, 600, 400);\n"
"chartSetTitle(chart, \"Visits\");\n"
"chartAddDataPoint(chart, \"Mon\", 12);\n"
"chartAddDataPoint(chart, \"Tue\", 18);\n"
"chartAddDataPoint(chart, \"Wed\", 9);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:544
msgid "Command palette (issue #477)"
msgstr "명령 팔레트 (issue #477)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:546
msgid ""
"⌘K-style fuzzy command launcher. macOS shows a floating `NSPanel`; other "
"platforms stub. Bind `commandPaletteShow()` to ⌘K via `addKeyboardShortcut` "
"to wire the default hotkey."
msgstr ""
"⌘K 스타일의 퍼지 명령 런처. macOS는 부동 `NSPanel`을 보여줍니다; 다른 플랫폼은 스텁. 기본 단축키를 배선하려면 "
"`addKeyboardShortcut`을 통해 `commandPaletteShow()`를 ⌘K에 바인딩하세요."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:550
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  commandPaletteRegister,\n"
"  commandPaletteShow,\n"
"} from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"commandPaletteRegister(\"save\", \"Save\", \"⌘S\", () => save());\n"
"commandPaletteRegister(\"export\", \"Export PDF\", \"\", () => exportPdf());\n"
"// then:\n"
"commandPaletteShow();\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:562
msgid "MapView (issue #517)"
msgstr "MapView (issue #517)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:564
msgid ""
"Wraps `MKMapView` on macOS / iOS / visionOS / tvOS, `libshumate` on GTK4, "
"Google Maps SDK on Android (requires API key in `AndroidManifest.xml`), and "
"the SwiftUI `Map` view on watchOS. Windows remains a stub (WinUI MapControl "
"needs XAML Islands integration)."
msgstr ""
"macOS / iOS / visionOS / tvOS의 `MKMapView`, GTK4의 `libshumate`, Android의 "
"Google Maps SDK (`AndroidManifest.xml`에 API 키 필요), watchOS의 SwiftUI `Map` 뷰를"
" 래핑합니다. Windows는 스텁으로 남아 있습니다 (WinUI MapControl은 XAML Islands 통합이 필요합니다)."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:569
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  MapView,\n"
"  mapViewSetRegion,\n"
"  mapViewAddPin,\n"
"  mapViewSetMapType,\n"
"} from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const map = MapView(800, 600);\n"
"mapViewSetRegion(map, 37.7749, -122.4194, 0.05, 0.05);\n"
"mapViewAddPin(map, 37.7749, -122.4194, \"San Francisco\");\n"
"mapViewSetMapType(map, 1); // 0=standard, 1=satellite, 2=hybrid\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:583
msgid "PdfView (issue #516)"
msgstr "PdfView (issue #516)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:585
msgid ""
"`PDFView` from PDFKit on macOS / iOS / visionOS. `pdfViewLoadFile` returns 1"
" on success, 0 on failure."
msgstr ""
"macOS / iOS / visionOS의 PDFKit에서 `PDFView`. `pdfViewLoadFile`은 성공 시 1, 실패 시 "
"0을 반환합니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:588
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  PdfView,\n"
"  pdfViewLoadFile,\n"
"  pdfViewGetPageCount,\n"
"} from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const pdf = PdfView(800, 600);\n"
"if (pdfViewLoadFile(pdf, \"/tmp/report.pdf\")) {\n"
"  console.log(\"pages:\", pdfViewGetPageCount(pdf));\n"
"}\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:601
msgid "RichTextEditor (issue #478)"
msgstr "RichTextEditor (issue #478)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:603
msgid ""
"`NSTextView` with `NSAttributedString` storage on macOS. Plain-text and HTML"
" round-trip cover persistence; `richTextToggleBold` / `ToggleItalic` / "
"`ToggleUnderline` cover inline formatting via `NSResponder` actions."
msgstr ""
"macOS에서 `NSAttributedString` 저장소가 있는 `NSTextView`. 일반 텍스트와 HTML 라운드트립이 지속성을 "
"다룹니다; `richTextToggleBold` / `ToggleItalic` / `ToggleUnderline`이 "
"`NSResponder` 액션을 통해 인라인 형식을 다룹니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:608
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import {\n"
"  RichTextEditor,\n"
"  richTextSetHtml,\n"
"  richTextGetHtml,\n"
"  richTextToggleBold,\n"
"} from \"perry/ui\";\n"
"\n"
"const editor = RichTextEditor(600, 400, (text) => console.log(text));\n"
"richTextSetHtml(editor, \"<p>Hello <b>world</b></p>\");\n"
"richTextToggleBold(editor);\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/widgets.md:621
msgid "Rich tooltip (issue #479)"
msgstr "리치 툴팁 (issue #479)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:623
msgid ""
"`widgetSetRichTooltip(widget, content, hoverDelayMs)` — like "
"`widgetSetTooltip` but the tooltip content is itself a Perry widget. macOS "
"uses `NSPanel` + `NSTrackingArea`; other platforms stub. For plain-text "
"tooltips with VoiceOver / a11y support, prefer the simpler "
"`widgetSetTooltip`."
msgstr ""
"`widgetSetRichTooltip(widget, content, hoverDelayMs)` — `widgetSetTooltip`과 "
"같지만 툴팁 콘텐츠 자체가 Perry 위젯입니다. macOS는 `NSPanel` + `NSTrackingArea`를 사용합니다; 다른 "
"플랫폼은 스텁. VoiceOver / a11y 지원이 있는 일반 텍스트 툴팁의 경우, 더 간단한 `widgetSetTooltip`을 "
"선호하세요."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:629
msgid "WebView (issue #658)"
msgstr "WebView (이슈 #658)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:631
msgid ""
"`WebView({ url, allowedDomains?, onShouldNavigate?, ... })` embeds a real "
"browser engine — `WKWebView` on Apple, `WebView2` on Windows, `WebKitGTK "
"6.0` on Linux, `android.webkit.WebView` on Android, sandboxed `<iframe>` on "
"web. See [WebView](webview.md) for the full OAuth / callback-interception "
"pattern and the per-platform notes."
msgstr ""
"`WebView({ url, allowedDomains?, onShouldNavigate?, ... })`는 실제 브라우저 엔진을 "
"내장합니다 — Apple에서는 `WKWebView`, Windows에서는 `WebView2`, Linux에서는 `WebKitGTK "
"6.0`, Android에서는 `android.webkit.WebView`, web에서는 샌드박스 처리된 `<iframe>`. OAuth"
" / 콜백 인터셉션 패턴 및 플랫폼별 참고사항은 [WebView](webview.md)를 참조하세요."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:637
msgid "These are linked from their own pages where richer examples exist."
msgstr "이들은 더 풍부한 예시가 존재하는 자체 페이지에서 링크됩니다."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:639
msgid "Common widget helpers"
msgstr "공통 위젯 헬퍼"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:641
msgid "Every widget handle accepts these:"
msgstr "모든 위젯 핸들은 다음을 받습니다:"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:643
msgid "Helper"
msgstr "헬퍼"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:645
msgid "`widgetSetWidth(w, n)` / `widgetSetHeight(w, n)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetWidth(w, n)` / `widgetSetHeight(w, n)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:645
msgid "Explicit size in points"
msgstr "포인트 단위의 명시적 크기"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:646
msgid "`widgetSetBackgroundColor(w, r, g, b, a)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetBackgroundColor(w, r, g, b, a)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:646
msgid "RGBA in \\[0, 1\\]"
msgstr "\\[0, 1\\]의 RGBA"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:647
msgid "`setCornerRadius(w, r)`"
msgstr "`setCornerRadius(w, r)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:647
msgid "Rounded corners in points"
msgstr "포인트 단위의 둥근 모서리"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:648
msgid "`widgetSetOpacity(w, alpha)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetOpacity(w, alpha)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:648
msgid "Opacity in \\[0, 1\\]"
msgstr "\\[0, 1\\]의 불투명도"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:649
msgid "`widgetSetEnabled(w, flag)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetEnabled(w, flag)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:649
msgid "`0` disables, `1` enables"
msgstr "`0` 비활성화, `1` 활성화"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:650
msgid "`widgetSetHidden(w, flag)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetHidden(w, flag)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:650
msgid "`0` visible, `1` hidden"
msgstr "`0` 보임, `1` 숨김"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:651
msgid "`widgetSetTooltip(w, text)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetTooltip(w, text)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:651
msgid "Tooltip on hover (desktop only)"
msgstr "호버 시 툴팁 (데스크톱 전용)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:652
msgid "`widgetSetOnClick(w, cb)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetOnClick(w, cb)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:652
msgid "Click handler"
msgstr "클릭 핸들러"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:653
msgid "`widgetSetOnHover(w, cb)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetOnHover(w, cb)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:653
msgid "Hover enter/leave (desktop only)"
msgstr "호버 enter/leave (데스크톱 전용)"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:654
msgid "`widgetSetOnDoubleClick(w, cb)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetOnDoubleClick(w, cb)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:654
msgid "Double-click handler"
msgstr "더블 클릭 핸들러"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:655
msgid "`widgetSetEdgeInsets(w, top, left, bottom, right)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetEdgeInsets(w, top, left, bottom, right)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:655
msgid "Padding around contents"
msgstr "콘텐츠 주위 패딩"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:656
msgid "`widgetSetBorderColor(w, r, g, b, a)` / `widgetSetBorderWidth(w, n)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetBorderColor(w, r, g, b, a)` / `widgetSetBorderWidth(w, n)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:656
msgid "Border"
msgstr "테두리"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:657 src/ui/layout.md:175
msgid "`widgetAddChild(parent, child)`"
msgstr "`widgetAddChild(parent, child)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:657
msgid "Attach a child to a container"
msgstr "컨테이너에 자식 첨부"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:658
msgid "`widgetSetContextMenu(w, menu)`"
msgstr "`widgetSetContextMenu(w, menu)`"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:658
msgid "Right-click menu"
msgstr "오른쪽 클릭 메뉴"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:660
msgid "See [Styling](styling.md) and [Events](events.md) for deeper coverage."
msgstr "더 깊은 다루기에 대해서는 [Styling](styling.md)과 [Events](events.md)를 참조하세요."

#: src/ui/widgets.md:664
msgid "[Layout](layout.md) — Arranging widgets with stacks and containers"
msgstr "[Layout](layout.md) — 스택과 컨테이너로 위젯 배치"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:665
msgid "[Styling](styling.md) — Colors, fonts, borders"
msgstr "[Styling](styling.md) — 색상, 폰트, 테두리"

#: src/ui/widgets.md:666 src/ui/theming.md:169
msgid "[State Management](state.md) — Reactive bindings"
msgstr "[State Management](state.md) — 반응형 바인딩"

#: src/ui/layout.md:3
msgid ""
"Perry provides layout containers that arrange child widgets using the "
"platform's native layout system. Every snippet below is excerpted from "
"[`docs/examples/ui/layout/snippets.ts`](../../examples/ui/layout/snippets.ts)"
" — CI compiles and runs it on every PR."
msgstr ""
"Perry는 플랫폼의 네이티브 레이아웃 시스템을 사용하여 자식 위젯을 배치하는 레이아웃 컨테이너를 제공합니다. 아래의 모든 스니펫은 "
"[`docs/examples/ui/layout/snippets.ts`](../../examples/ui/layout/snippets.ts)에서"
" 발췌되었습니다 — CI는 모든 PR에서 그것을 컴파일하고 실행합니다."

#: src/ui/layout.md:8
msgid ""
"Layout helpers are free functions: `widgetAddChild(parent, child)`, "
"`stackSetAlignment(stack, value)`, `widgetSetEdgeInsets(w, top, left, "
"bottom, right)`, etc. Stack constructors take a numeric spacing followed by "
"a child array; everything else (alignment, distribution, padding, sizing) is"
" applied post-construction via the free functions on the widget handle."
msgstr ""
"레이아웃 헬퍼는 자유 함수입니다: `widgetAddChild(parent, child)`, "
"`stackSetAlignment(stack, value)`, `widgetSetEdgeInsets(w, top, left, "
"bottom, right)` 등. 스택 생성자는 자식 배열 다음에 수치 spacing을 받습니다; 그 외 모든 것 (정렬, 분배, 패딩,"
" 자식 변경)은 컨테이너 핸들을 받는 자유 함수입니다."

#: src/ui/layout.md:14 src/platforms/watchos.md:54 src/platforms/android.md:34
#: src/platforms/linux.md:48 src/widgets/components.md:43
msgid "VStack"
msgstr "VStack"

#: src/ui/layout.md:16
msgid "Arranges children vertically (top to bottom)."
msgstr "자식을 수직으로 배치합니다 (위에서 아래로)."

#: src/ui/layout.md:18
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"const stack = VStack(16, [\n"
"    Text(\"First\"),\n"
"    Text(\"Second\"),\n"
"    Text(\"Third\"),\n"
"])\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:26
msgid ""
"`VStack(spacing, children)` — the first argument is the gap in points "
"between children."
msgstr "`VStack(spacing, children)` — 첫 번째 인수는 자식 사이의 포인트 단위 간격입니다."

#: src/ui/layout.md:29 src/platforms/watchos.md:55 src/platforms/android.md:35
#: src/platforms/linux.md:49 src/widgets/components.md:52
msgid "HStack"
msgstr "HStack"

#: src/ui/layout.md:31
msgid "Arranges children horizontally (left to right)."
msgstr "자식을 수평으로 배치합니다 (왼쪽에서 오른쪽으로)."

#: src/ui/layout.md:33
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"const row = HStack(8, [\n"
"    Button(\"Cancel\", noop),\n"
"    Spacer(),\n"
"    Button(\"OK\", noop),\n"
"])\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:41 src/platforms/watchos.md:56 src/platforms/android.md:36
#: src/platforms/linux.md:50 src/widgets/components.md:62
msgid "ZStack"
msgstr "ZStack"

#: src/ui/layout.md:43
msgid ""
"Layers children on top of each other (back to front). `ZStack()` takes no "
"constructor children — populate it with `widgetAddChild`:"
msgstr ""
"자식을 서로 위에 레이어링합니다 (뒤에서 앞으로). `ZStack()`은 생성자 자식을 받지 않습니다 — `widgetAddChild`로"
" 채우세요:"

#: src/ui/layout.md:46
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"const layered = ZStack()\n"
"widgetAddChild(layered, ImageFile(\"background.png\"))\n"
"widgetAddChild(layered, Text(\"Overlay text\"))\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:52 src/platforms/macos.md:35 src/platforms/ios.md:61
#: src/platforms/tvos.md:60 src/platforms/watchos.md:62
#: src/platforms/android.md:37 src/platforms/windows.md:54
#: src/platforms/linux.md:51 src/testing/geisterhand.md:94
msgid "ScrollView"
msgstr "ScrollView"

#: src/ui/layout.md:54
msgid ""
"A scrollable container. Built empty, then filled via `scrollviewSetChild`:"
msgstr "스크롤 가능한 컨테이너. 비어 있게 빌드된 다음 `scrollviewSetChild`를 통해 채워집니다:"

#: src/ui/layout.md:56
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// ScrollView() takes no args; populate it with `scrollviewSetChild`.\n"
"const sv = ScrollView()\n"
"const inner = VStack(8, [Text(\"a\"), Text(\"b\"), Text(\"c\")])\n"
"scrollviewSetChild(sv, inner)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:63
msgid "LazyVStack"
msgstr "LazyVStack"

#: src/ui/layout.md:65
msgid ""
"A vertically scrolling list that lazily renders items. More efficient than "
"`ScrollView` + `VStack` for thousands of rows — on macOS this is backed by "
"`NSTableView` so only rows in the visible rect are realized."
msgstr ""
"항목을 지연 렌더링하는 수직 스크롤 목록. 수천 행에는 `ScrollView` + `VStack`보다 더 효율적입니다 — macOS에서는"
" 이것이 `NSTableView`로 지원되어 보이는 사각형의 행만 실현됩니다."

#: src/ui/layout.md:69
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// `render(index)` is invoked lazily — only rows in the visible rect are realized.\n"
"const lazy = LazyVStack(1000, (index: number) => Text(`Row ${index}`))\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:74
msgid ""
"When the underlying data changes, call `lazyvstackUpdate(handle, newCount)` "
"to refresh. Override the default 44pt row height with "
"`lazyvstackSetRowHeight`."
msgstr ""
"기본 데이터가 변경되면 `lazyvstackUpdate(handle, newCount)`를 호출하여 새로 고치세요. 기본 44pt 행 "
"높이를 `lazyvstackSetRowHeight`로 재정의하세요."

#: src/ui/layout.md:77
msgid "NavStack"
msgstr "NavStack"

#: src/ui/layout.md:79
msgid ""
"A navigation container that supports push/pop navigation. Push a new view "
"with `navstackPush(stack, view, title)`; pop with `navstackPop(stack)`:"
msgstr ""
"푸시/팝 네비게이션을 지원하는 네비게이션 컨테이너. `navstackPush(stack, view, title)`로 새 뷰를 푸시; "
"`navstackPop(stack)`으로 팝:"

#: src/ui/layout.md:82
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"const home = VStack(16, [\n"
"    Text(\"Home Screen\"),\n"
"    Button(\"Go to Details\", () => {\n"
"        navstackPush(nav, Text(\"Details!\"), \"Details\")\n"
"    }),\n"
"])\n"
"const nav = NavStack()\n"
"widgetAddChild(nav, home)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:93 src/platforms/watchos.md:57
#: src/widgets/components.md:71 src/widgets/platforms.md:25
#: src/widgets/platforms.md:26
msgid "Spacer"
msgstr "Spacer"

#: src/ui/layout.md:95
msgid "A flexible space that expands to fill available room."
msgstr "사용 가능한 공간을 채우기 위해 확장하는 유연한 공간."

#: src/ui/layout.md:97
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"const toolbar = HStack(8, [\n"
"    Text(\"Left\"),\n"
"    Spacer(),\n"
"    Text(\"Right\"),\n"
"])\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:105
msgid "Use `Spacer()` inside `HStack` or `VStack` to push widgets apart."
msgstr "위젯을 떨어뜨리려면 `HStack` 또는 `VStack` 내에서 `Spacer()`를 사용하세요."

#: src/ui/layout.md:107 src/platforms/watchos.md:58
#: src/widgets/components.md:106 src/widgets/platforms.md:26
msgid "Divider"
msgstr "Divider"

#: src/ui/layout.md:109
msgid "A visual separator line."
msgstr "시각적 분리선."

#: src/ui/layout.md:111
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"const sections = VStack(12, [\n"
"    Text(\"Section 1\"),\n"
"    Divider(),\n"
"    Text(\"Section 2\"),\n"
"])\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:119
msgid "Nesting Layouts"
msgstr "레이아웃 중첩"

#: src/ui/layout.md:121
msgid "Layouts can be nested freely. This complete example is verified by CI:"
msgstr "레이아웃은 자유롭게 중첩할 수 있습니다. 이 완전한 예시는 CI로 검증됩니다:"

#: src/ui/layout.md:123
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// demonstrates: nested VStack/HStack + Spacer + Divider\n"
"// docs: docs/src/ui/layout.md\n"
"// platforms: macos, linux, windows\n"
"// targets: ios-simulator, web, wasm\n"
"\n"
"import { App, VStack, HStack, Text, Button, Spacer, Divider } from \"perry/ui\"\n"
"\n"
"App({\n"
"    title: \"Layout Example\",\n"
"    width: 800,\n"
"    height: 600,\n"
"    body: VStack(16, [\n"
"        // Header\n"
"        HStack(8, [\n"
"            Text(\"My App\"),\n"
"            Spacer(),\n"
"            Button(\"Settings\", () => {}),\n"
"        ]),\n"
"        Divider(),\n"
"        // Content\n"
"        VStack(12, [\n"
"            Text(\"Welcome!\"),\n"
"            HStack(8, [\n"
"                Button(\"Action 1\", () => {}),\n"
"                Button(\"Action 2\", () => {}),\n"
"            ]),\n"
"        ]),\n"
"        Spacer(),\n"
"        // Footer\n"
"        Text(\"v1.0.0\"),\n"
"    ]),\n"
"})\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:158
msgid "Child Management"
msgstr "자식 관리"

#: src/ui/layout.md:160
msgid "Containers support dynamic child management via free functions:"
msgstr "컨테이너는 자유 함수를 통해 동적 자식 관리를 지원합니다:"

#: src/ui/layout.md:162
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"const list = VStack(16, [])\n"
"widgetAddChild(list, Text(\"appended\"))            // append\n"
"widgetAddChildAt(list, Text(\"prepended\"), 0)      // insert at index\n"
"widgetReorderChild(list, 1, 0)                    // move from→to\n"
"const removeMe = Text(\"temporary\")\n"
"widgetAddChild(list, removeMe)\n"
"widgetRemoveChild(list, removeMe)                 // remove\n"
"widgetClearChildren(list)                         // remove all\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

