"const buttons = HStack(8, [\n"
"    Button(\"Cancel\", noop),\n"
"    Button(\"OK\", noop),\n"
"])\n"
"stackSetDistribution(buttons, 1) // FillEqually — both buttons get equal width\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/layout.md:221 src/container/networking.md:143
