msgid ""
"[Single-container lifecycle](./containers.md) — every `perry/container` call"
" documented with examples."
msgstr ""
"[단일 컨테이너 수명 주기](./containers.md) — 예제와 함께 문서화된 모든 `perry/container` 호출."

#: src/container/overview.md:193
msgid ""
"[Compose orchestration](./compose.md) — `perry/compose` and the "
"`ComposeSpec` shape, including the canonical TS-object pattern."
msgstr ""
"[Compose 오케스트레이션](./compose.md) — `perry/compose`와 `ComposeSpec` 형태, 표준 TS "
"객체 패턴 포함."

#: src/container/overview.md:195
msgid ""
"[Networking](./networking.md) — networks, the `internal` flag, and the "
"cross-service-DNS gotcha (and how to work around it today)."
msgstr ""
